<keyLead pageId="10" pageNumber="77">
1a. 
<emphasis box="[211,272,623,644]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="77">Plants</emphasis>
small, epiphytic; 
<emphasis box="[439,499,623,644]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="77">leaves</emphasis>
basally cuneate; 
<emphasis box="[661,729,623,644]" italics="true" pageId="10" pageNumber="77">corolla</emphasis>
colour variable (red through orange to pinkish orange to yellow or yellowish green), generally more intensely coloured than in 
<taxonomicName authorityName=", Baker" authorityYear="1883" box="[689,866,651,672]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Crassulaceae" genus="Kalanchoe" kingdom="Plantae" order="Saxifragales" pageId="10" pageNumber="77" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="peltata">
